title: Blueline bugreport for Pixel 4XL is showing "Warning:" for every bugreport processed. Is it nornal??
content:
Every bugreport processed is showing "Warning" and a message that either the directory can't be located/doesn't exist, or some other issue.  Is this normal?  If not, what should my next steps be?

For whatever reason I'm unable to attach the saved report - perhaps if you're knowledgable of this issue and willing, you might advise if a means to send a copy of said report.

Thank you.
